      "content": "exactly. that's what i mean. like, why would they give me *more* power if they were trying to hide things? it feels like they're just trying to put me in a gilded cage where they can watch everything i do. i feel like the office itself is designed to be monitored. even the way my new assistant acts... it's like she's reporting back to compliance every time i leave my desk. you think they'd actually go that far just to keep an eye on one person?",
