      "content": "it's actually getting scary. i noticed there's a new smart speaker in my office that wasn't there before, and i keep getting these 'security updates' for my laptop at weird hours. i'm starting to feel like i can't even trust my own devices. if they are really trying to build this surveillance state around me, what kind of things should i be looking out for? how do i know if they've already tapped into my personal phone or something?",
